OL,3,CLaundrette mugger foiled by pensioner
OL,4,Carmed with jeans jailed
OL,6,FA mugger who was fought off by an 84-
OL,7,Fyear-old pensioner brandishing a pair
OL,8,Fof jeans in a laundrette has been
OL,9,Fjailed.
OL,11,FLloyd Smith, 42, demanded cash from
OL,12,FRon Croker after confronting him as he
OL,13,Fused the Coin-Op Launderette in
OL,14,FMaltby, near Rotherham, on 7 January.
OL,16,FIn CCTV footage which later went viral
OL,17,Fon social media, Mr Croker could be
OL,18,Fseen wrapping a pair of his jeans
OL,19,Faround his arm, fearing Smith was
OL,20,Fcarrying a knife.
