OL,6,FSmith was arrested two days later but
OL,7,Fclaimed that he was not the man in the
OL,8,FCCTV footage.
OL,10,FHowever, he pleaded guilty to
OL,11,Fattempted robbery when he appeared at
OL,12,FSheffield Crown Court in February.
OL,14,FAt his sentencing hearing on Tuesday,
OL,15,Fthe court heard Smith had a cocaine
OL,16,Fhabit and a history of more than 70
OL,17,Fprevious offences.
OL,19,FHe was was jailed for three years and
OL,20,Fnine months.
